data.title: Tommy Davidson
data.meta_description:
​From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia.  

Tommy Davidson (born November 10, 1963) is an American comedian, film and television actor.

Born in Washington, D.C., Davidson was adopted when he was 2-years-old. He is the product of an interracial adoption, with his parents being Caucasian and he being African-American. He attended high school at Bethesda-Chevy Chase High School, in Bethesda, Maryland...
